  "8LWpeBX6ZwY": [
    {
      "text": "This is the Coalition Emergency Broadcast System.",
      "start": 4.8,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": "There are reports of multiple tremors causing minor damage across Colona.",
      "start": 10,
      "duration": 5.8
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Stay sharp. Don't let them surround you.",
      "start": 18.56,
      "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
      "text": ">> There should be more guns in the trunk. >> Here. Strap these on.",
      "start": 24.04,
      "duration": 6.72
    },
    {
      "text": ">> This isn't enough. We should still head to the police station. We're going to have more firepower there. >> Right. >> Yeah. >> It's about two blocks up ahead. >> Okay. >> Come on. >> Shoot, move, AND WATCH FOR CIVILIANS.",
      "start": 33.04,
      "duration": 14.96
    },
    {
      "text": "GET inside now.",
      "start": 51.44,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [screaming] >> Ground's opening.",
      "start": 58.295,
      "duration": 4.825
    },
    {
      "text": ">> There's too many.",
      "start": 78.32,
      "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
      "text": "Henry! Henry, where are you? >> [screaming]",
      "start": 82.56,
      "duration": 5.265
    },
    {
      "text": ">> You see that? It was something big. Like huge track fingers digging up through the street. Just the adrenaline hit. We need to keep moving. Through the underpass. >> Let's get moving.",
      "start": 102,
      "duration": 14.72
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Let me see what I can do.",
      "start": 117.24,
      "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
      "text": ">> I'm at the Pay 'n' Save. I need backup.",
      "start": 120.76,
      "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
      "text": "These things are all over me. >> More tremors. >> Any Gears out there, anyone that can hear this?",
      "start": 125,
      "duration": 7.679
    },
    {
      "text": "Look out! >> Oh, [\u00a0__\u00a0] What the [\u00a0__\u00a0] IS THAT?",
      "start": 140.52,
      "duration": 5.439
    },
    {
      "text": ">> TARGET SIGHTED. OPEN FIRE.",
      "start": 148.12,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": ">> THESE ARE GODDAMN breach points.",
      "start": 162.88,
      "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Reloading. Cover me.",
      "start": 173.52,
      "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [screaming]",
      "start": 180.127,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning]",
      "start": 182.747,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> All right. That Gear said they're stuck in the Pay 'n' Save. Which way? >> It's on the other side of those apartments. At least that thing [music] carved us a shortcut.",
      "start": 185.44,
      "duration": 12.76
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Through here.",
      "start": 198.32,
      "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Who's there?",
      "start": 204.84,
      "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
      "text": "AH, BUGGER. COME ON, MAN.",
      "start": 209.4,
      "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
      "text": "What the hell? Oh. Nice shot. Oh. Where the hell did you lot come from? >> We heard your distress call. >> Well, you saved my ass. But we need to make ourselves scarce. These [\u00a0__\u00a0] keep pouring in every few minutes.",
      "start": 214.16,
      "duration": 18.2
    },
    {
      "text": "More tremors. >> Watch it. >> RIGHT ON SCHEDULE. YOU GUYS HERE? >> YEAH. Who are you? >> I'M WITH THE MILITIA. >> WHERE'S YOUR SQUAD? >> They sent me to scout out THE SWARM OF MONSTERS. WE WERE PROTECTING SOME survivors nearby. I'm about to get back to the corner of the hill.",
      "start": 234.4,
      "duration": 22.24
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [groaning] >> Reloading. Cover.",
      "start": 263.312,
      "duration": 3.688
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Take tomorrow. These things been coming in waves. >> Ah, I got a problem cuz I ran out of ammo. I'm loading heavy artillery. I got friends on my side.",
      "start": 268.52,
      "duration": 11.28
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [groaning]",
      "start": 284.928,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning and screaming] >> Eat that. >> Nah. >> Throwing a grenade.",
      "start": 289.513,
      "duration": 7.127
    },
    {
      "text": ">> They come. Watch your back.",
      "start": 297.76,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": ">> RELOADING.",
      "start": 304,
      "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
      "text": ">> DIE.",
      "start": 310.48,
      "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
      "text": ">> GOT TO RELOAD.",
      "start": 317.32,
      "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> ANYONE SEE HIM?",
      "start": 320.2,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": ">> CONTACT FRONT. >> THERE'S NO END TO THESE FREAKS.",
      "start": 323.72,
      "duration": 5.48
    },
    {
      "text": ">> PICK THEM OFF. >> ON YOUR RIGHT, PARTNER. >> I got it.",
      "start": 337.44,
      "duration": 6.68
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Jammed. >> DAMN IT. >> HEY. >> [screaming]",
      "start": 347.32,
      "duration": 5.128
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning]",
      "start": 362.219,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[screaming]",
      "start": 368.769,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning] >> DOM. >> I'M ALMOST THERE. I'M almost there.",
      "start": 372.044,
      "duration": 6.636
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [groaning]",
      "start": 387.109,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Our roads converge again.",
      "start": 392.64,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": "Marcus Fenix.",
      "start": 396.76,
      "duration": 3.12
    }
  ],
  "z1CWk2Ft884": [
    {
      "text": "I could get used to this. Feels like we're miles away from the cast. >> The army. They'll see our boat as soon as they arrive. What's our plan? Well, we've got the book. We know the island better than they do. >> Oh, we're so close, Lenny. We can slip away before they catch sight of us. Believe me, I can feel it. There's something on this island.",
      "start": 10.719,
      "duration": 30.68
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm the key. >> The thief's here, you as she's got the sphere. If we catch her, we'll get a better share of the loot. >> U pirate. Sort out. >> Careful. You cut yourselves.",
      "start": 57.68,
      "duration": 16.36
    },
    {
      "text": "I'll make it sl",
      "start": 82.159,
      "duration": 3.64
    },
    {
      "text": "Are you hurt? No. Let's move before more come.",
      "start": 88.08,
      "duration": 7.079
    },
    {
      "text": "The wave bird. What? Still thinking of a name for our future boat. Is now the right time? >> It's never the right time.",
      "start": 101.52,
      "duration": 11.72
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Strange seeing everything the gang left behind. >> They thought they'd be back soon.",
      "start": 122.88,
      "duration": 7.239
    },
    {
      "text": "Jesus. >> Cuz come at me. >> Did you really think you could sneak in like that? >> Doesn't look like we tried to.",
      "start": 153.76,
      "duration": 10.96
    },
    {
      "text": "Shut this one up, sir.",
      "start": 169.04,
      "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
      "text": ">> I'll make sure you scream.",
      "start": 176.4,
      "duration": 4.199
    },
    {
      "text": "What happened here?",
      "start": 203.599,
      "duration": 3.801
    },
    {
      "text": "God, I didn't realize how big it was.",
      "start": 214.08,
      "duration": 5.159
    },
    {
      "text": "I should write these down.",
      "start": 223.92,
      "duration": 4.039
    },
    {
      "text": ">> What now?",
      "start": 235.68,
      "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
      "text": "I can use this to find our way through.",
      "start": 246.319,
      "duration": 4.441
    },
    {
      "text": "These were made of glass in the fresco room, right? Must have been put here on purpose.",
      "start": 261.6,
      "duration": 6.599
    },
    {
      "text": "Did they have to make everything so damn complicated?",
      "start": 283.36,
      "duration": 4.68
    },
    {
      "text": "Holy hell.",
      "start": 298.32,
      "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Did they not have any sense of scale? Clearly not.",
      "start": 302.88,
      "duration": 6.28
    },
    {
      "text": ">> This is",
      "start": 309.28,
      "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
      "text": "Heat. Heat.",
      "start": 341.28,
      "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
      "text": "Heat. Heat. Heat.",
      "start": 346.88,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Where the hell am I?",
      "start": 383.28,
      "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh god, I need to breathe.",
      "start": 398.16,
      "duration": 6.2
    },
    {
      "text": "Just a bit further.",
      "start": 413.759,
      "duration": 3.481
    },
    {
      "text": "the monster. It's not real.",
      "start": 424.08,
      "duration": 4.839
    }
  ],
  "Zv5kk_Ck65k": [
    {
      "text": "Akashima Island >> [music] >> haunted by dark stories. Our goal >> [music] >> confront the evil corrupting paradise. This is Dead True International.",
