      "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [music]",
      "start": 34.06,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Over. Rotated on that one. >> A for effort, dude. [music] >> Who's the buff idiot? >> Does no one know this guy?",
      "start": 38.04,
      "duration": 9.44
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [music] >> Oh, you two haven't met yet, right? >> Sebastian. I've been looking out for you.",
      "start": 51.745,
      "duration": 7.255
    },
    {
      "text": "Roll whenever you're ready. >> This facility [music] has been shut down for decades. Uninvestigated, untold until now.",
      "start": 59.6,
      "duration": 11.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Did you hear that?",
      "start": 75.88,
      "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Nate. Are you out there?",
      "start": 79.16,
      "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Jesus. [\u00a0__\u00a0]",
      "start": 83.28,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": ">> We got to go.",
      "start": 88.6,
      "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Run. >> [music] >> I have a bad feeling. >> Let's get rid of that. >> Grip it tight. >> Go. He's coming. Through there. >> Take a deep breath. >> [\u00a0__\u00a0] Which way? >> Skinny, [music] the mine. >> We're going to have TO JUMP. >> THERE'S ROCKS DOWN THERE.",
      "start": 92,
      "duration": 17.92
    },
    {
      "text": ">> GO. GO.",
      "start": 111.2,
      "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [screaming]",
      "start": 114.626,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> CAN YOU DO WHAT NEEDS to be done?",
      "start": 118.44,
      "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
      "text": ">> PlayStation",
      "start": 140.88,
      "duration": 3.0
    }
